snippet.title: Rocket racing with @MaxG4k - Twitch Plays Conway's Game of Life - Classic Edition (Unity3d ECS)
snippet.description:
Play Conway's Game of Life by typing commands in the Twitch chat: https://www.twitch.tv/bzh314
@MaxG4k (https://www.twitch.tv/maxg4k) used the !RLE command to create a 117P9H3V0 (http://www.conwaylife.com/wiki/117P9H3V0), a period-3 spaceship that looks like a rocket. Is it faster than the 74P8H2V0 rocket?
The Run Length Encoded command for the 117P9H3V0:
!rle 8bo8b$7bobo7b$6bo3bo6b$7b3o7b2$5b2o3b2o5b$2b2o3bobo3b2o2b$2b2o3bobo3b2o2b$2o5bobo5b2o$4b2obobob2o4b$o6bobo6bo$3b2o2bobo2b2o3b$bo2bobo3bobo2bob$b2o11b2ob$b2o11b2ob$4bo7bo4b$4b3o3b3o4b$6bo3bo6b$3b2obo3bob2o3b$5b2o3b2o5b$5bobobobo5b2$5bo2bo2bo5b$6b2ob2o6b$5b2o3b2o5b2$4bo2b3o2bo4b$3b11o3b$3b2obo3bob2o! 0,0
The Run Length Encoded command for the 74P8H2V0:
!rle 5bobobo$4b7o$4bo5bo$5bo3bo$5bo3bo$3b2o5b2o$5bo3bo$2bobobobobobo$4bobobobo$b2obobobobob2o$bo3b2ob2o3bo2$2o3bo3bo3b2o$5bo3bo$6b3o2$4bo4b2o$3bobo2b2o$6bo2bobo$3bo2bo2bobo$4bobo3bo! -32.0

More:
* VOD with chat commands: https://www.twitch.tv/videos/310144373
* Homepage of Twitch Plays Conway's Game of Life: https://bzh314.com/twitch_plays_conway_game_of_life/
* Play Now on #Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/bzh314
